17
00:01:13,546 --> 00:01:15,615
<font color=#FFFF00>...selain Universitas Nasional Namhae.</font>

18
00:01:15,916 --> 00:01:17,356
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahnya bilang biaya hidup
