43
00:02:32,756 --> 00:02:34,266
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sehari sebelum hari pertama...,</i></font>

44
00:02:35,726 --> 00:02:37,935
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Namhae - Seoul]</i></font>

45
00:02:38,566 --> 00:02:40,036
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dia minggat saat malam hari.</i></font>

46
00:02:43,506 --> 00:02:44,976
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Universitas Nasional Namhae]</i></font>

47
00:02:51,576 --> 00:02:52,976
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, dah.</font>

48
00:02:56,346 --> 00:02:57,916
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Di mana kau? Ayah di
depan gerbang kampusmu. Keluarlah.]</i></font>

49
00:03:08,826 --> 00:03:11,236
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sampai semester pertamanya
selesai, ayahnya Ji Ho...</i></font>

50
00:03:11,236 --> 00:03:13,196
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...mengira Ji Ho itu kuliah
di Universitas Namhae.</i></font>

51
00:03:14,736 --> 00:03:16,435
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia memang gila.</font>

52
00:03:17,775 --> 00:03:19,736
<font color=#FFFF00>Padahal kukira si Soo Ji
ini yang paling gila.</font>

53
00:03:19,736 --> 00:03:22,606
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, Soo Ji ini cuma
kepribadiannya yang jelek.</font>

54
00:03:23,615 --> 00:03:24,816
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau Yoon Ji Ho...,</font>

55
00:03:25,245 --> 00:03:28,386
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia selalu mengejutkanmu
pada saat yang paling tak terduga.</font>

56
00:03:32,856 --> 00:03:35,625
<font color=#FFFF00>Ahjussi-nya lagi kesal, jadi
dia tak mau menunggu lama-lama.</font>

57
00:03:35,826 --> 00:03:37,395
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi cepat, jawab aku, ya.</font>

58
00:03:38,096 --> 00:03:39,196
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

59
00:03:39,296 --> 00:03:40,666
<font color=#FFFF00>Maukah kau...</font>

60
00:03:41,326 --> 00:03:42,525
<font color=#FFFF00>...menikah denganku?</font>

61
00:03:45,335 --> 00:03:48,106
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepat. Dia lagi menunggu.</font>

62
00:03:50,136 --> 00:03:51,205
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

63
00:03:51,536 --> 00:03:53,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, kuambil
koperku, ya.</font>

64
00:03:54,106 --> 00:03:56,006
<font color=#FFFF00>Soalnya, Ahjussi itu
lagi kesal sekali.</font>

65
00:03:57,245 --> 00:03:58,346
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf.</font>

66
00:04:00,346 --> 00:04:02,085
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada yang harus kutanyakan sebelumnya.</font>

67
00:04:02,245 --> 00:04:03,786
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, tanya saja.</font>

68
00:04:04,155 --> 00:04:05,386
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa mungkin, kau...</font>

69
00:04:09,356 --> 00:04:10,726
<font color=#FFFF00>...menyukaiku?</font>

70
00:04:14,196 --> 00:04:15,266
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

71
00:04:16,125 --> 00:04:18,296
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa barangmu.
Kutunggu kau di dalam.</font>

72
00:04:38,385 --> 00:04:41,956
<font color=#FFFF00>Kuperhatikan kau mencuci
mangkuk ramyeon-nya.</font>

73
00:04:43,656 --> 00:04:45,596
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, aku sudah biasa begitu.</font>

74
00:04:46,726 --> 00:04:49,695
<font color=#FFFF00>Kebiasaanmu sangat bagus sekali.</font>

75
00:04:50,865 --> 00:04:52,096
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

76
00:04:53,805 --> 00:04:55,765
<font color=#FFFF00>Sayang, ada tempat duduk.
Kau, duduklah./ Tidak, kau saja.</font>

77
00:04:55,765 --> 00:04:57,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak apa, kau saja
yang duduk.</font>

78
00:04:57,836 --> 00:04:58,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Mana tasmu.</font>

79
00:04:59,606 --> 00:05:01,805
<font color=#FFFF00>Rambutmu bagus./
Bagus, 'kan?</font>

80
00:05:02,305 --> 00:05:03,875
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku kegerahan./
Gerah?</font>

81
00:05:09,385 --> 00:05:10,555
<font color=#FFFF00>Duduklah.</font>

82
00:05:11,115 --> 00:05:12,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau saja yang duduk duluan.</font>

83
00:05:12,856 --> 00:05:13,986
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

84
00:05:42,745 --> 00:05:44,015
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku kini...</i></font>

85
00:05:45,286 --> 00:05:48,425
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...akan menikah dengan
majikan rumah.</i></font>

86
00:05:59,736 --> 00:06:01,606
<font color=#FFFF00>Syaratku masih belum berubah.</font>

87
00:06:02,906 --> 00:06:04,276
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau ada yang keberatan?</font>

88
00:06:07,646 --> 00:06:11,015
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau soal syaratmu, tak ada.</font>

89
00:06:12,875 --> 00:06:16,146
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa mungkin ada
yang ingin kau tambahkan?</font>

90
00:06:18,185 --> 00:06:21,986
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti yang sudah kau tahu,
aku sudah berhenti bekerja.</font>

91
00:06:23,356 --> 00:06:25,596
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi sebelum aku dapat
pekerjaan baru...,</font>

92
00:06:27,166 --> 00:06:30,026
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku butuh penyesuaian
dengan uang sewanya.</font>

93
00:06:32,466 --> 00:06:35,736
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa tidak uang sewanya
diturunkan sedikit?</font>

94
00:06:36,635 --> 00:06:38,675
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa banyak?</font>

95
00:06:40,846 --> 00:06:42,075
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekitar 50 ribu.</font>

96
00:06:43,075 --> 00:06:44,646
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau kau bisa menurunkannya...,</font>

97
00:06:45,346 --> 00:06:47,815
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku takkan terlalu
berat membayarnya.</font>

98
00:06:54,026 --> 00:06:56,185
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, baiklah.</font>

99
00:06:57,026 --> 00:07:00,325
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, kontrak kita,
250 ribu sebulan.</font>

100
00:07:00,666 --> 00:07:03,226
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik. Terima kasih.</font>

101
00:07:05,765 --> 00:07:07,406
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau yakin bisa mengatasinya?</font>

102
00:07:10,606 --> 00:07:11,706
<font color=#FFFF00>Maksudku, pernikahan.</font>

103
00:07:13,646 --> 00:07:16,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Di situasi seperti ini, mungkin
lebih ekonomis...</font>

104
00:07:16,445 --> 00:07:18,315
<font color=#FFFF00>...jika pulang ke rumah.</font>

105
00:07:20,716 --> 00:07:21,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

106
00:07:23,346 --> 00:07:26,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalaupun aku pulang,
aku masih harus cari pekerjaan.</font>

107
00:07:28,456 --> 00:07:32,656
<font color=#FFFF00>Apalagi, aku nanti bakal
bertengkar sama Ayah.</font>

108
00:07:34,226 --> 00:07:36,296
<font color=#FFFF00>Satu-satunya perbedaan antara
pulang dan disini 'kan cuma uang sewa.</font>

109
00:07:37,135 --> 00:07:39,995
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak akan ada tempat
yang lebih baik dari Seoul.</font>

110
00:07:40,836 --> 00:07:42,305
<font color=#FFFF00>Di Namhae pun, susah
cari kerja.</font>

111
00:07:44,276 --> 00:07:46,945
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya tingkat stres
di luar biaya sewa.</font>

112
00:07:48,675 --> 00:07:50,916
<font color=#FFFF00>Walau begitu, aku tadi
agak kaget.</font>

113
00:07:52,115 --> 00:07:55,615
<font color=#FFFF00>Kukira kau menganggap pernikahan
itu didasarkan pada cinta.</font>

114
00:07:56,385 --> 00:07:58,755
<font color=#FFFF00>Waktu kau memilih pernikahan
berdasarkan persewaan...,</font>

115
00:07:59,055 --> 00:08:02,086
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku sangat kaget.</font>

116
00:08:03,486 --> 00:08:04,695
<font color=#FFFF00>Hanya saja...</font>

117
00:08:05,796 --> 00:08:07,565
<font color=#FFFF00>Sama seperti katamu...,</font>

118
00:08:08,765 --> 00:08:12,666
<font color=#FFFF00>...cinta dan kasih sayang...</font>

119
00:08:15,565 --> 00:08:18,375
<font color=#FFFF00>...bukan hal yang kubutuhkan
sekarang ini.</font>

120
00:08:19,805 --> 00:08:23,505
<font color=#FFFF00>Yang kubutuhkan sekarang adalah
kamar itu.</font>

121
00:08:25,445 --> 00:08:27,815
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku, hari ini, memutuskan
akan menikahi penyewaku.</i></font>

122
00:08:29,515 --> 00:08:30,656
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku sadar.</i></font>

123
00:08:31,755 --> 00:08:34,726
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ini bukan keputusan biasa
yang dilakukan orang kebanyakan.</i></font>

124
00:08:37,295 --> 00:08:38,655
<font color=#FFFF00>Malah, sebenarnya...,</font>

125
00:08:41,566 --> 00:08:43,295
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku juga sangat ingin...</font>

126
00:08:45,365 --> 00:08:46,836
<font color=#FFFF00>...mencobanya sekali.</font>

127
00:08:48,905 --> 00:08:50,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Pernikahan.</font>

128
00:08:51,106 --> 00:08:52,905
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku akhirnya menemukan...</i></font>

129
00:08:55,676 --> 00:08:57,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah mengurutkan
penyortiran minggu ini?</font>

130
00:08:59,275 --> 00:09:01,216
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...seorang wanita yang sangat
tak biasa sebagai istriku.</i></font>

131
00:09:04,915 --> 00:09:08,486
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Episode 3: Karena ini
Pernikahan Pertamaku]</i></font>

132
00:09:31,115 --> 00:09:32,446
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh...</font>

133
00:09:34,245 --> 00:09:35,645
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidur nyenyak sekali.</font>

134
00:10:09,446 --> 00:10:10,915
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat pagi.</font>

135
00:10:11,385 --> 00:10:12,486
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

136
00:10:16,556 --> 00:10:18,155
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mau?</font>

137
00:10:18,395 --> 00:10:21,265
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tadi kebanyakan
buat sarapannya.</font>

138
00:10:21,265 --> 00:10:25,295
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak perlu. Secangkir americano sudah
cukup baik buat sarapan pagiku.</font>

139
00:10:26,336 --> 00:10:27,466
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

140
00:10:54,295 --> 00:10:55,525
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Enaknya.</i></font>

141
00:10:55,966 --> 00:10:57,995
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Makanan dan malamku juga.</i></font>

142
00:10:58,395 --> 00:11:01,736
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku sudah lama tak mengalami pagi
seindah ini.</i></font>

143
00:11:02,336 --> 00:11:03,976
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sama seperti kata pepatah.</i></font>

144
00:11:04,635 --> 00:11:06,736
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku tidak bisa menopang
diriku sendiri.</i></font>

145
00:11:07,005 --> 00:11:09,775
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Di keadaan seperti ini, mana
bisa aku berkencan dan mencintai?</i></font>

146
00:11:10,245 --> 00:11:12,346
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Uang 5 juta buat sewaan
saja, aku tak punya.</i></font>

147
00:11:12,446 --> 00:11:15,415
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Namun berkat pernikahan ini, aku
dapat diskon 50 ribu.</i></font>

148
00:11:15,486 --> 00:11:17,785
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dalam dua tahun, berapa
jadinya itu?</i></font>

149
00:11:20,785 --> 00:11:23,226
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Keputusan tepat, Yoon Ji Ho.</i></font>

150
00:11:26,495 --> 00:11:29,596
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Nyamannya. Kitty dan aku.</i></font>

151
00:11:30,795 --> 00:11:33,135
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku sudah lama tak mengalami
akhir pekan yang tenang.</i></font>

152
00:11:35,336 --> 00:11:37,635
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku tidak harus menderita
ikut kencan buta lagi...</i></font>

153
00:11:38,436 --> 00:11:40,905
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dan tertekan soal
penyortiran barang-barang.</i></font>

154
00:11:41,806 --> 00:11:45,076
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dengan memberikan diskon 50 ribu,
aku menjadi tenang.</i></font>

155
00:11:47,415 --> 00:11:49,946
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tadi pakai telur.</font>

156
00:11:49,946 --> 00:11:51,456
<font color=#FFFF00>Nanti kubeli lagi telurnya.</font>

157
00:11:52,216 --> 00:11:53,316
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

158
00:12:06,535 --> 00:12:10,535
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sudah kuduga. Menikah dengan penyewaku
memang solusinya.</i></font>

159
00:12:14,176 --> 00:12:15,476
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, ini Ji Ho.</font>

160
00:12:16,706 --> 00:12:18,816
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Hari ini, ya?</font>

161
00:12:19,576 --> 00:12:21,946
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh. Baiklah.</font>

162
00:12:22,346 --> 00:12:24,155
<font color=#FFFF00>Nanti aku datang malam ini.</font>

163
00:12:24,515 --> 00:12:26,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Semoga selamat sampai tujuan.</font>

164
00:12:27,285 --> 00:12:28,385
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

165
00:12:29,385 --> 00:12:30,795
<font color=#FFFF00>Dari orang tuamu?</font>

166
00:12:31,125 --> 00:12:35,696
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Ada acara pernikahan,
jadi mereka datang ke Seoul.</font>

167
00:12:36,295 --> 00:12:40,135
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa aku harus pergi
ke rumah adikku malam ini.</font>

168
00:12:40,466 --> 00:12:43,165
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, apa
aku harus ikut denganmu?</font>

169
00:12:43,836 --> 00:12:45,976
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Kenapa?</font>

170
00:12:46,206 --> 00:12:48,976
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau kita akan menikah, aku harusnya
berkenalan dengan orang tuamu.</font>

171
00:12:50,816 --> 00:12:51,946
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar juga.</font>

172
00:12:52,216 --> 00:12:54,885
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus seperti itu
jika kita mau menikah.</font>

173
00:12:55,045 --> 00:12:59,086
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Sebenarnya aku sudah
mengatur alur prosesnya semalam.</font>

174
00:12:59,586 --> 00:13:00,856
